						<p><hi rend="bold">King: ⎯⎯ Year 20, 178th day.</hi></p>						

						<p>In characters of the 12th century A.D. This inscription registers a gift of one thousand <hi rend="italic">kāśu by</hi> Kurukatti-uḍaiyāṉ Tirumākaḷam-uḍaiyāṉ Sambandaṉ <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Mājanapiriyaṉ, the accountant of the village <hi rend="italic">(ūr-kaṇakku)</hi> Kulōttuṅgachōḻachaturvēdimaṅgalam in Puṟaṅkarambai-nāḍu, for burning a twilight lamp.</p>						

